You promised to take it slow.

421
00:20:05,872 --> 00:20:08,457
Eddie, I forgot what it's like
dealing with you.

422
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:10,001
You blew it!

423
00:20:10,084 --> 00:20:11,919
I'm really angry. Go!

424
00:20:12,378 --> 00:20:16,090
First of all, I have never been
